itemDescription: Turks and Caicos Islands association football player (born 1986)

wikipedia_page.main: James Rene (born 2 February 1986) is a Turks and Caicos Islander international footballer who plays for the Turks and Caicos Islands national football team, as a defender.

response: Beginning in 2016, Fenelus managed Provo Premier League club Full Physic, alongside fellow Turks and Caicos international James Rene.
